Where dessert lovers roll in for the viral banana pudding and leave pudding their trust in one of Ottawa’s sweetest cravings. 🍌🍨

If you’ve been scrolling through Ottawa food TikTok or IG looking for viral banana pudding, chances are you’ve already seen this spot. Happy Rolls Dessert Bar is known for serving up creamy, nostalgic banana pudding layered with fresh bananas, vanilla wafers, and clouds of sweet cream that basically peel away your self-control.

And while the classic banana pudding is the viral star, I decided to go slightly bananas and try the cookie butter version… because sometimes you just have to roll with the sweeter plot twist. 🍪🍌

✨ Dessert Highlights
• Viral Banana Pudding — creamy layers, fresh bananas &amp; vanilla wafers 🍌✨
• Cookie Butter Banana Pudding — the Biscoff-y twist that’s pudding up a fight for favourite 🤎
• Fresh layered dessert cups made for the ultimate sweet tooth moment 🍨
• A must-visit Ottawa dessert spot for viral food lovers &amp; late-night treat runs 🌙

💸 Sweet Treat Pricing
• Banana Pudding Cups – around $10
• Cookie Butter Banana Pudding – around $11
• Rotating dessert creations &amp; specialty treats available in-store 🍧

Because life’s too short to split dessert… sometimes you just have to pudding yourself first. 🍌💁‍♀️ Would you try this spot?

